== Emacs keybindings ==

Opera can do this too, even though it's not
documented anywhere. On a unix system with Opera, choose Tools -> Preferences
-> Mouse and Keyboard -> Opera Standard for Unix.

[http://my.opera.com/csant/blog/2007/06/11/emacs-keyboard-bindings-2 Here] is a blog entry for even better Emacs keys for Opera

